              },
              "free_text": [
                " U-400M cyclotron and ACCULINNA fragment",
                "separator were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The primary 15N beam with an energy of 49.7 A MeV was",
                "focused on the production 9Be target. The secondary",
                "beam of fragmentation reaction products was formed",
                "and purified by the magnetic system of the fragment",
                "separator."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "DeltaE detector (natural Si, 790 mu-m thick) was used",
                "as a target."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A system of deltaE detectors was used."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The scintillation detectors of the spectrometer",
                "registered prompt gamma quanta and neutrons."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TOF",
                "GSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 4pi method with CsI(Tl) gamma",
                "spectrometer was used."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TRN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Measurements were conducted both with the target",
                "and without the target to measure the background."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "An empirical correction 'eta' (sigmaR=sigmaR/eta) was",
                "introduced. It takes into account not only the",
                "anisotropy of neutron emission but also the",
                "contribution of the elastic breakup channel which is",
                "not accompanied by gamma radiation."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The effective matter radii of the 11,12Be and 14B",
                "nuclei were determined."
              ]
            }
          ],
